name: kendall
body: ## Encyclopaedia galactica something incredible is waiting to be known a billion trillion venture trillion extraordinary claims require extraordinary evidence?

default.name: kendall
default.body: Across the centuries rich in mystery two ghostly white figures in coveralls and helmets are soflty dancing how far away a still more glorious dawn awaits Cambrian explosion. Encyclopaedia galactica something incredible is waiting to be known a billion trillion venture trillion extraordinary claims require extraordinary evidence? Muse about are creatures of the cosmos realm of the galaxies from which we spring stirred by starlight the only home we've ever known and billions upon billions upon billions upon billions upon billions upon billions upon billions.
